Author: loversalibi
Text: i’m not trying to be rude but honestly if your parents were CHANTING “give up” they’re actual pieces of fucking shit   fuck them. never give up. you may have slipped up but you can do this.

Author: Belarie
Text: That sounds so triggering. I’m rooting for you. It’s not all completely ruined just because you purged once. You still have the destination, the steps you did take have put you closer to your path on being b/p free.  You can message me if you need someone to talk to, anytime. :)
